products

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • products.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Invoice, Order

    public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Product is Java class used to instantiate objects that constitute various merchandised products for transactions on the shopping site. A Product object encapsulates the information needed to describe a product, such as its category, image png or jpg, ID, description and price.
